title: Fushi Yami
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Japanese, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Japanese restaurant serving sushi, habachi entrees, and yakisoba noodles. The menu includes a specific vegetable sushi section with 10 vegetarian choices, of which some may be vegan or could possibly be made vegan. There are additional vegetarian appetizers, yakisoba, and habachi items on the menu; again, some may be vegan or could possibly be made vegan. Vegans please inquire.
